    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what people say, isn't it? \"hope,\" \"support\"... it all feels so hollow. it's not like there's some big bright future waiting for me. it's just more days of sitting in this silence. it feels like the part of me that actually lived died with him. everything else is just... going through the motions. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
